  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Inclusiveness of Persons with Disability in 4 Municipal/District Assemblies of the V/R</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.Conduct a monthly direct radio advocacy broadcast on disability
2.Development of information and Educational material on disability
3.Conduct Capacity building of PWDs&#x2019; representatives atAssembly and DPOs on planning and budgeting enhance effective participation
4.Mapping and field tracking of the implementation of Disability projects and enforcement of disability policies in four District Assemblies</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Increased PWDs in decision making processes and participation in all the stages of the Assembly decision making processes, e.g during the Composite budget preparation. 
 Increase inclusiveness and accessibility needs of PWDs in the Assembly 
The broader issue of gender equality and social inclusion is at the core of this project. Hence the project through conceptualization, design and activities to be carried out will actively consider gender equality issues.</narrative>
  </description>
